OL,3,CWHO declares global health emergency
OL,4,Cover Ebola outbreak in Congo and Uganda
OL,6,FThe World Health Organization has
OL,7,Fdeclared the Ebola disease outbreak in
OL,8,FCongo and Uganda a public health
OL,9,Femergency of international concern on
OL,10,FSunday after more than 300 suspected
OL,11,Fcases and 88 deaths.
OL,13,FIn a post on X, the World Health
OL,14,FOrganization (WHO) said the outbreak
OL,15,Fdoes not meet the criteria of a
OL,16,Fpandemic emergency like the Covid-19
OL,17,Fpandemic, and advised against the
OL,18,Fclosure of international borders.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
