OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779045069
OL,3,CWHO declares global health emergency
OL,4,Cover Ebola outbreak in Congo and Uganda
OL,6,FCongo accounts for all except two of
OL,7,Fthe cases, both of which were reported
OL,8,Fin neighbouring Uganda, the WHO said.
OL,10,FOfficials first reported the spread of
OL,11,Fthe disease in Congo's eastern
OL,12,Fprovince of Ituri, close to Uganda and
OL,13,FSouth Sudan, on Friday.
OL,15,FOn Saturday, the Africa Centres for
OL,16,FDisease Control and Prevention
OL,17,Freported 336 suspected cases and 87
OL,18,Fdeaths.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
