OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779045069
OL,3,CWHO declares global health emergency
OL,4,Cover Ebola outbreak in Congo and Uganda
OL,6,F"There are significant uncertainties
OL,7,Fto the true number of infected persons
OL,8,Fand geographic spread associated with
OL,9,Fthis event at the present time. In
OL,10,Faddition, there is limited
OL,11,Funderstanding of the epidemiological
OL,12,Flinks with known or suspected cases,"
OL,13,FWHO Director-General Tedros Adhanom
OL,14,FGhebreyesus said.
OL,16,FUganda on Saturday confirmed one case
OL,17,Fit said was imported from Congo, and
OL,18,Fsaid the patient died at a hospital in
OL,19,FUganda's capital, Kampala, and the WHO
OL,20,Fsaid that a second case has been
OL,21,Freported in Kampala.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
