OL,3,CWHO declares global health emergency
OL,4,Cover Ebola outbreak in Congo and Uganda
OL,6,FWHO's emergency declaration is meant
OL,7,Fto spur donor agencies and countries
OL,8,Finto action. However, the global
OL,9,Fresponse to previous declarations has
OL,10,Fbeen mixed.
OL,12,FIn 2024, when the WHO declared mpox
OL,13,Foutbreaks in Congo and elsewhere in
OL,14,FAfrica a global emergency, experts at
OL,15,Fthe time said it did little to get
OL,16,Fsupplies like diagnostic tests,
OL,17,Fmedicines and vaccines to affected
OL,18,Fcountries quickly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
